properties.areaDesc: Lake Michigan from Seul Choix Point to Rock Island Passage 5NM offshore to Mid Lake; Lake Michigan South of a line from Seul Choix Point to the Mackinac Bridge and North of a line from Charlevoix MI to South Fox Island 5NM offshore; Lake Michigan from Charlevoix to Point Betsie MI 5NM Offshore to mid lake; Lake Michigan from Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI 5NM offshore to mid lake
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 25 at 3:05PM CST until January 25 at 4:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Areas of dense fog will reduce visibility to 1 mile or
much less.

* WHERE...Lake Michigan north of a line from 5 NM offshore
Sturgeon Bay to 5 NM offshore Point Betsie MI.

* WHEN...Until 4 PM CST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM CST THIS AFTERNOON
